g.text: Define candidateAbscissa(1) by inverse polynomial interpolation of fv, v, fw, w, and fx, x.candidateAbscissa(2) = x + e*shrinkFactor;perturbed = candidateAbscissa;perturbFactor = Sign(e)/2;sameTestAbscissas = {x,u,c,a,w,v};

g.text: Select from perturbed a list containing only the first perturbed abscissa between a and c that represents displacement less than maxAcceptableDisplacement from x. Call the list newAbscissa. It will be empty if no points match the criteria.
